-388636882.text: "Mechanistically, p62 induces hypoxia-inducible-factor 1alpha (HIF1alpha) signaling though the upregulation of mTORC1 and NF-kappaB activity, and the downregulation of VHL E3 ubiquitin ligase activity, thus inducing HIF1alpha activation, glucose uptake and lactate production, and growth in soft agar."
